To recap

reviewText:
First of all cons of the game:
Each level is a long LOOONG LOOOOOONG glorified corridor with lots and lots and lots and lots of repetitive mobs ;

Also, I would've liked (personally) to see some melee combat, I mean, if you're the badass mage you're suppose to be, why not go full-badass and become the true DRAGON" aka go all Rand Al'Thor on your enemies
